data.text:
Manama, March 03 (QNA) - The Director of Staff in Bahrain National Guard, Major-General Sheikh Abdulaziz bin Saud Al Khalifa met here today with the Commandant General of British Royal Marines Major-General Martin Smith and his accompanying delegation.

According to Bahrain News Agency (BNA) ,the two sides reviewed bilateral relations between the two countries in addition to issues of common interest. Sheikh Abdulaziz affirmed that his country's aspiration for further military cooperation between the two sides and ways to develop this cooperation through the exchange of experiences and conducting joint exercises between the two sides. (QNA)
